flowchart LR
    %% Direction: put user on the far left
    U[User]

    subgraph AWS["AWS account"]
        R53[Amazon Route 53]
        CF[Amazon CloudFront]
        S3[Amazon S3]
        APIGW[Amazon API Gateway]
        ACM[AWS Certificate Manager]
        L1[AWS Lambda - ingest and API handler]
        SQS[Amazon SQS]
        L2[AWS Lambda - worker and processor]
        DDB[Amazon DynamoDB]
    end

    %% Static site and result delivery
    U -->|DNS lookup | R53
    R53 -->|Alias to distribution| CF
    CF -->|Cached assets and results| U
    S3 -->|Origin reads| CF

    %% API entry and job creation
    R53 -->|api dot your domain - custom domain| APIGW
    ACM -.->|TLS cert for custom domain - HTTPS| APIGW

    APIGW -->|POST jobs - invoke| L1
    L1 -->|PutItem UpdateItem - job metadata and status| DDB
    L1 -->|SendMessage - enqueue job| SQS
    APIGW <-.->|GET jobs id - poll status| L1
    L1 -.->|Query status| DDB
    APIGW -->|202 Accepted plus job id| U

    %% Async processing
    SQS -->|Event source mapping - batches retries DLQ| L2
    L2 -->|Write outputs and artifacts| S3
    L2 -.->|Optional cache invalidation or signed URL generation| CF
    L2 -->|Update status| DDB